        {
            "title": "退稅與能源成本上升:對美國消費者有何影響?",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ae3OCk7O4eJ3aGUyWhp_pA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_3_M_1440048334.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 報稅季即將結束,儘管最初樂觀的消費支出前景正變得充滿挑戰。雖然退稅金額遠高於去年,稅務負擔大致保持穩定,但燃料成本的飆升抵消了大部分提振效果,高盛認為未來幾個月實際消費增長將疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年資本利得稅支付增加的影響可能被去年根據《一項大型美好法案》(OBBBA)推出的財政方案所抵消。退稅金額比去年高出17%,而目前的稅款支付可能最終比去年增加400億至550億美元。這仍比若非OBBBA而會出現的800億美元增幅低250億至400億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5a61a8fb-5844-3ed9-b7b7-edb5b504edd4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本報稅季收到的稅款顯示,稅款支付低於預期。高盛表示:「一個使用股市回報、房屋銷售和資金流動數據預測非預扣稅款的模型顯示,這些支付應比去年高出14%,即截至5月中旬約800億美元。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與去年同期相比,稅單大致持平,而OBBBA帶來的總收益預計在750億至900億美元之間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於去年財政方案帶來的稅收優惠在規模上與當前資本利得稅支付的增加大致相當,對消費支出的淨影響將微乎其微。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結果是,消費支出的推動力有限。稅收減免實際上被能源通脹所抵消。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">談到能源成本,自戰爭開始以來,汽油價格已上漲40%。按目前水平計算,這相當於美國家庭收入每年約1400億美元的逆風。高盛預計,到年底這一逆風將按年化基礎縮減至600億美元,但2026年全年總計將達700億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得注意的是,汽油價格上漲對最低收入五分之一家庭的負擔最重。這些家庭在汽油上的支出佔稅後收入的比例,約為最高收入五分之一家庭的四倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這也將對可自由支配支出類別造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據油價預測,高盛預計實際可支配收入將按第四季度對第四季度基礎增長1.6%,或全年增長1.2%。實際消費增長預計將按第四季度對第四季度基礎增長1.2%,或全年增長1.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">減稅帶來的好處已被汽油價格上漲所吸收。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%80%E7%A8%85%E8%88%87%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-184156328.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-26 02:52:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛稱韓國股市有望繼續跑贏美國股市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 高盛分析師認為,韓國綜合股價指數(<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"KOSPI\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:KOSPI;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/KOSPI\">KOSPI</a>)看來將繼續跑贏<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國股市\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國股市;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國股市\">美國股市</a>指數,儘管韓國最近宣布了回流投資帳戶政策,對海外股票的資本利得稅提供減免或豁免。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這導致帳戶總數增至16萬個,回流投資帳戶總餘額達7.06億美元。該機構表示,隨著散戶投資者資金回流韓國,自2月以來流入美國的散戶投資資金出現減弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在2025年上漲76%之後,KOSPI今年迄今已上漲50%,遠遠跑贏標普500指數今年迄今4.47%的漲幅。美國指數的典型回報率在10-20%區間。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d8d1bc3a-0cc7-3e4d-8b11-9082e35be635-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">KOSPI創下歷史新高,單週上漲4.6%,受好於預期的第一季GDP和不斷擴大的市場廣度推動。儘管製藥、保險和證券板塊表現最差,但造船、機械和科技板塊在過去一週表現出色。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外國投資者拋售KOSPI市場,主要是因為科技和汽車板塊出現資金外流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">值得注意的是,散戶投資者在美國股市仍持有超過1,770億美元。此外,2026年迄今,散戶投資者流入追蹤韓國國內股市的ETF的資金已超過追蹤外國股市的ETF。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">強勁的散戶資金流入國內股市、政策推動的資本回流,以及從美國ETF轉向韓國ETF的趨勢,共同支持了KOSPI有望跑贏美國股市指數的論點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月稍早,摩根大通觀察到,在伊朗衝突造成干擾之前,韓國股市是全球最熱門的市場。現在,復甦似乎已經完成,KOSPI綜合指數正朝著創紀錄水平再次邁進。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人工智能需求推動的半導體超級週期、盈利上調,以及強勁的外資流入韓國科技公司,共同創造了一條增長軌跡,可以產生高於美國股市的相對回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在記憶體晶片和國防板塊的推動下,這種增長強化了KOSPI相對於美國股市的高貝塔值、高上行潛力特徵。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E7%A8%B1%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82-164904947.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-26 01:45:06",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德國海軍部隊為潛在霍爾木茲海峽任務做準備",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國將向地中海派遣海軍部隊，為可能在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>執行國際任務做準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們將向地中海部署一艘掃雷艦，並為其配備一艘指揮補給艦，」德國國防部長皮斯托裡烏斯在《萊茵郵報》周六發布的採訪中表示。他沒有具體說明兩艘船何時啟航。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">皮斯托裡烏斯強調，該地區敵對行動的結束是德國任何軍事部署的先決條件。他還指出，只有議會批准，這樣的部署才有可能實現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">皮斯托裡烏斯說：「為了節省時間，我們決定儘早將部分德國部隊部署到地中海，這樣一旦任務授權獲得批准，我們就不會再浪費時間。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c2728a79-fe7f-3e41-ba9c-e037f2513d30-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">皮斯托裡烏斯在採訪中稱，「我們的海軍在探測和清除水雷方面非常出色。」他補充說：「我們可以以此為保障霍爾木茲海峽的自由和安全航行作出貢獻。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：德國總理稱支持保障霍爾木茲海峽航道安全 但需聯合國授權</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Germany Readies Naval Units for Possible Hormuz Mission (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
